list.name: Default
list.comment: Some incremental major restructuring to the folders of the engine. I put the source code into the src folder, all resources in the resources folder and delete some old decrepate folders.

task.summary: Fixed file path locations to UNIX standard. Need to replace glm, not compiling.
Made a lot of fixes to the code, specifically fixing Logger issues and adding a pre-proccesor variable whether or not to include Fonts.
Added OpenGL and GLEW libraries to the cmake for linux compiling.

Added bullet3 libs and sources under /lib/bullet3/ I havent changed the include files to bullet3 yet.
Added #define BT_USE_DOUBLE_PRECISION 1 before including bullet. Won't compile with g++ otherwise.
Added library source codes including their .a, .so objects
Added Assimp and finished compilation issues.
Loads textures, shaders and other resources.
Physics engine is giving us some difficulties, keeps crashing the game everytime the setSimulation is called.
Deleted the bullet3 folder in lib
Added bullet3 libs in separate folder. For some reason anything in bullet3 will not be uploaded.
Random OpenGL bug that prevented stuff from being displayed. Traced the bug to the camera which is not properly sending the view matrix.
Got stuff to show up. Still need to fix the cameras view matrix. Might be a problem with glm::lookat function.
Added windows libs to the target link libraries
Some incremental major restructuring to the folders of the engine. I put the source code into the src folder, all resources in the resources folder and delete some old decrepate folders.
